{"tid":1393242,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩見到巴打呢張陣形圖","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T05:49:28.000Z","uid":206522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"097610047f5e3a39c3ed9acd5f03f18b6511d3e7","tid":1393242,"uid":206522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCgq39T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCgq39T.png&h=df01b79c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人認為幾好<br />\n但我覺得應該要分開無數小隊形式進行<br />\n<br />\n如果太大隊，有狗過黎捉人<br />\n好多時會有責任分散效應<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/p6yxlm2.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fp6yxlm2.amp&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5wUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=c380f4df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/p6yxlm2.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n咁好多人會以為其他人會去救人，咁最後手足可能變到冇人救<br />\n<br />\n而小隊制式可以將救人最大責任綁定番係某幾個人身上，而全隊有危機再請求其他隊伍幫忙，對機動性，撤退，進攻戰略都好有幫助<br />\n<br />\n最好每小隊都有溝通/指揮做各小隊協調<br />\n<br />\n小隊行動方針跟隨指令員<br />\n可減少撤退 進攻 決定上既混亂"},{"pid":"f157f00bc3951f7fe15d34f59d640b98cfc9ceac","tid":1393242,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"仲有弓兵"},{"pid":"85bb6cb9f118fce339987c94a41245cccf831feb","tid":1393242,"uid":286222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:49:28.000Z","msg":"2005年, 韓農來港的反世貿示威, 對抗警察幾有效果"}]}